{"tid":40975,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"朗尼毀牆焚宮 魔性盡現","createTime":"2016-12-15T14:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T01:01:13.000Z","uid":12034,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1cc84d753074d04caac3edf0316b7875441401","tid":40975,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=516e0b3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周三對水晶宮一戰，曼聯隊長朗尼疑因不滿未獲判12碼，被換出後在後備席發脾氣，以球靴大力打向玻璃，並聽到碎裂聲。<br />\n朗尼（Wayne Rooney）周中為曼聯落場鬥水晶宮，戰至80分鐘比數仍是1:1時被換出，幸8分鐘後隊友伊巴謙莫域攻入奠勝1球，為紅魔全取3分。該名曼聯隊長仍在場上時，就因球證包臣一次沒判罰12碼的決定，感到憤怒。 儘管他及後被換出，但從電視片段所見，仍然怒氣未消，竟把球鞋脫掉，猛力打向後備席的玻璃。1次還不止，當他擊打第2次時，也許是力度過猛，後備席玻璃就應聲碎裂，此舉亦驚動了坐在其身前的曼聯領隊摩連奴，摩佬隨即對他念念有詞，似乎在說：「你在搞甚麼？」 摩佬事後亦有解釋情況：「他（朗尼）為一記可能是12碼的問題球感到憤怒，在後備席向第4球證投訴，他為此很不高興，但<span style=\"color: red;\">即使是賽和1:1，我也會對他說：『忘記吧，忘記它吧。』</span>」 相關片段： <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7658teB1g1E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7658teB1g1E&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=f39249c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7658teB1g1E</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BX8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=087be393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華，請按此<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朗尼型到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c912d010a0c5281e6ebbf85f45d6313a3b70dd5d","tid":40975,"uid":47852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:15:10.000Z","msg":"忘記吧，忘記它吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5e19dab5b86edfb7cd947137eafb660bbe838e","tid":40975,"uid":5843,"like":0,